            "stanza_text": "Bin bam, bin bam,\nLes cloches, les cloches,\nChansons en l'air, pauvres reproches !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 4,
                    "line_text": "Petits et gros, clochers en fête,",
