                    "line_text": "Car il descend ! Il descend !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Bons vitraux, saignez impuissants\nAux allégresses hosannahlles\nDes orgues lâchant leurs pédales,\nLes tuyaux bouchés par l'encens !\nCar il descend ! Il descend !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Voici les lentes oriflammes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Où flottent la Vierge et les Saints !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Les cloches, leur battant des mains,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "S'étourdissent en jeunes gammes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Hymniclames ! Hymniclames !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Voici les lentes oriflammes\nOù flottent la Vierge et les Saints !\nLes cloches, leur battant des mains,\nS'étourdissent en jeunes gammes\nHymniclames ! Hymniclames !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Va, Globe aux studieux pourchas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Où Dieu à peine encor s'épèle !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Bondis, Jérusalem nouvelle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Vers les nuits grosses de rachats,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Où les lys ne filent pas !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Va, Globe aux studieux pourchas,\nOù Dieu à peine encor s'épèle !\nBondis, Jérusalem nouvelle,\nVers les nuits grosses de rachats,\nOù les lys ne filent pas !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Édens mûrs, Unique Bohême !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Nous, les beaux anges effrénés ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Elles, les Regards incarnés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Pouvant nous chanter, sans blasphème :",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Que je t'aime ! Pour moi-même !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Édens mûrs, Unique Bohême !\nNous, les beaux anges effrénés ;\nElles, les Regards incarnés,\nPouvant nous chanter, sans blasphème :\nQue je t'aime ! Pour moi-même !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Oui, les cloches viennent de loin !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Oui, oui, l'Idéal les fit fondre",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Pour rendre les gens hypocondres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Vêtus de noir, tendant le poing",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Vers un Témoin ! Un Témoin !",
